narratives.question_text: What was the name of your practicum instructor?
comments: Susan Fowler is an excellent resource for spiritual formation. Her comments really helped my guide my next steps.

I found it very difficult to discuss my daily prayer with someone else. It is personal and a private activity. It is also difficult to share this with a stranger and resisted doing so because of my faith conviction. Instructor was very supportive and understanding. I have a concern about this part of the course and grading policy.

narratives.question_text: What were her/his strengths or weaknesses?
comments: Her calmness and deep spirituality were appreciated!
Meditation/ prayer was very helpful. Instructor is very sincere and always ready and willing to help students.
She participated in classes with devotionals. Very enlightening.
